@bellahadid is focused on being present—and her two newest scents for her perfume line, @orebella, encompass just that.
Candied Sand and Neroli’s Halo (called the Solars) are about “moving forward,” she tells ELLE’s @ktberohn. “In a lot of our previous scents, I always spoke of nostalgia. With these newest ones, I want people to feel like they’re in the present. It’s about feeling at home within yourself.” Like all of the ‘Ôrəbella scents, these two mists have a unique bi-phase formula that has to be shaken to “activate.” But unlike some of the other fragrances, the Solars have a higher water concentration, so they feel more like refreshing spritzes than traditional perfumes—Hadid calls them “fresh to death.”
At the link in bio, Hadid talks to ELLE about keeping the new scents in her ATV, her daily wellness lineup, and the It book that she’s reading right now.

